title: 820-4924 just s5 rails
message:
SMC_ADAPTER_EN 0v and seems to be shorted to ground 3.2 ohm.
Removed R5185 still shorted.
Replaced SMC but measured SMC_ADAPTER_EN without SMC in place and still short.
Anything else then PCH that can short this line ?

title: 820-4924 just s5 rails
message:
Check for corrosion at R5185.
Not probably, but is the only thing you can check.
Because the other suspect is PCH (CPU).

I hope you measured resistance to ground without power applied...
